<p class="ql-align-justify">小时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想挣脱大人的手</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">长大后</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">却抓不住父母的手</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">岁月是瓶老酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸甜苦辣全在心头</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">你曾经对人的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如今只能一个人承受</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">人生的旅途</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后一个人走</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再好的夫妻</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">进入各自梦里头</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在夜阑人静的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">回望做过的事</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没有迷失在人性沙丘</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">哪怕自己受伤难受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201108/d11fd32bbbc84346b5864ce2d5098ffc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>漂泊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>文\草根一一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果时光流成河</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">逃避往事</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">就去漂泊</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不管内心苦涩</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不管花朵</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有一个梦就足够</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">穿过朦朦胧胧的河</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">唱着莫名的歌</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没有眼泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">没有笑容</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">慢慢地泅过</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">青春在靠岸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我试想对面</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有日月 女人和酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">音乐在引诱我</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我能拒绝自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但不能拒绝寂寞</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我上岸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是为了无意义的</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被洗白的记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是为了被风浪</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">拍打的魂灵</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">上岸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是无奈与自主的选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我收好思想的帆</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我脱下满身风尘</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我开始回味</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">回味漂泊</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那些自由曾属于我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201108/17344ca9060b4dc2b8582f74a7544a08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>生活中的随笔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一畦小菜惹人爱，心有田园花自开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">可怜步梯数不够，路灯照影独徘徊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201108/37b2b16707ce4658b9d05758398f8831.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">邻城的夕阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">可曾记得</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">白天</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">穿裙子的姑娘</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吮吸冰糕的孩童</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喝茶论天下的男人</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">刚好一幅冬日暖阳图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201108/08bd4c32e5b54c70b2719d6689f4078d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">地上</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有一些黑鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在游弋</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">搁浅在日光之城</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">影子摩擦欲念</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">身体在噼噼啪啪生长</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我不是窗外的</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那棵树</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在光合作用</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">滤清病毒邪恶</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">叶子深呼吸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">根须思如梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">让明亮更亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">让黑暗透光</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">让生命力飞扬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201108/e6d3d3eb92b4450d8c0d5a9b1ff65ebd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">你追逐太阳，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我追逐你，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">至夕阳西下。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">你牵着你左手，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我牵着我右手，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一起回家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">追光者黑崎子</p>
